(1, 'About Us', '<div class=\"transition-content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(33, 35, 38); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.6px;\"><main id=\"MainContent\" class=\"content-for-layout focus-none shopify-section\" role=\"main\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; box-shadow: none !important; outline: 0px !important; transition: transform var(--duration-long) ease;\"><section id=\"shopify-section-template--15236446683268__16624427404f4938e9\" class=\"shopify-section section\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><div class=\"page-width section-template--15236446683268__16624427404f4938e9-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; max-width: var(--page-width); margin: 0px auto; padding: 36px 5rem;\"><div class=\"img-txt\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; width: 780.625px;\"><blockquote style=\"line-height:1.4666666666666668;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6f877853-7fff-afa1-5c53-119c42cea63d\"><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:27pt;font-family:Arial;color:#323232;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We are not magicians, just</span></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:27pt;font-family:Arial;color:#323232;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">really passionate</span></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-2892a9ac-7fff-2c73-9d1e-e08f338cad58\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#646464;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We are a young enthusiastic team, working behind the scenes to invite you into the secret life of plants. To nudge you to experiment, make mistakes, play, pause, and disconnect from the noise and find your centre, trying our best to earn the smile you wear on seeing the healthy, happy plants you receive</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#646464;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:200px;height:183px;\"><img alt=\"about us\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/JAtHZzFhUiaKGHhBGmeHH3Q3Mqqvf4rPe3BuNfFfjPhmWK6pxBdFFC1WQa0cK6ijJt_NAO-LeTF-MGj1djH6tSlZHSXXfQ7TM3_CBQMUoQ3DaVT9dCQ254IT-uRo9ICSAlBF7eaN2-bLRQgHE0ZvYuBUnKH7x1Bi1j_WIQeUU3oF4ozYCkmxVSCrCShd-Q\" width=\"200\" height=\"183\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><br></b></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:27pt;font-family:Arial;color:#323232;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Why we started BayLeaf</span></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#646464;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">BayLeaf was formed with the idea to help people pause and breathe in some peace in their busy city lives.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#646464;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Bayleaf sprung up like a new leaf on a spring morning and is today a mighty tree that helps other smaller businesses thrive in its shade. We have formed a proudly Made in India ecosystem that grows with each passing day.</span></p><br></b></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:27pt;font-family:Arial;color:#323232;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">What we do</span></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#646464;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We are here to encourage people to discover beauty, miracles, and serendipity in their everyday lives. We are here to make the magic of plants accessible to you at your fingertips and safeguard and nurture them till they reach you - their forever homes.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#646464;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We make plant parenting simpler, comfortable, less intimidating and reassuring through our ideas, knowledge, and understanding. We grow our plants with passion, happiness, and utmost care so that when they reach you, they spread the same joy in your lives.</span></p><br></b></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:27pt;font-family:Arial;color:#323232;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">How we do it</span></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We are driven by our passion to promote the slower way of life, to help you find the small joys that life has to offer. We grow our own plants in state-of-the-art polyhouses and greenhouses spread over 18 acres of land. Our people watch over the plants with expert help and guidance from planting to transporting them to your doorstep.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We use a science backed approach to grow our plants, adhere to sustainable practices to the best of our ability, while growing a community of growers and small business owners that grow with us on this journey.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:701px;height:276px;\"><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/RCSYCCc8X-d8iR4XXdBkIW48ayTjiOn77_vJK9YfyXy90njAFqAANbNZS8CYxn7FoLrty-K7cKg5ut1H4X8NgMzifyu7EIY4whYDhI7pMmQmIowPRLl-iymfzV_IHm3uxUeOGWp-oe3FOKnDh18hPqgSD55wl6t70HsTr2BZ1gvPmq9n6DY6ItfqHay__A\" width=\"728.2987484236463\" height=\"276\" style=\"margin-left:-19.807500126903715px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><br><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">UNDERSTANDING THE LANDSCAPE</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We spoke to lots of plant parents - newbies, experts, dabblers, hobbyists to understand their relationship with plants.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Through experts and influencer interviews in the fields of home gardening, sustainability, plant care we understood movements and tipping points for urban gardening.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We carried out an extensive secondary culture research to understand more culture shifts as well as consumer and category codes from Indian and international markets.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">EMERGING CULTURAL SHIFTS</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Urban consumers across markets, especially millennials were already navigating worsening burnouts, lifestyle stresses and wondering how to escape the matrix of work, always-on connectivity and alienation.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The simultaneously terrifying and isolating nature of the pandemic coupled with geopolitical climate disasters (often all connected) further contributed to different experiences of burnout, a sense of being â€˜doneâ€™ and an all-pervasive need to make lasting changes to oneâ€™s personal environment, health, habits and wellbeing.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:624px;height:107px;\"><img alt=\"ugaoo_strat-all\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/swEzU-ZA2PFo0zpr87avPRqxPZMBo0kUOm8o-BmdwRYcIiOdYM7tnsMBAyJQNAKYt_lQXm4-ADcvfFgxEekpyybLMWn1j9wgxS3tlqoP8QUb6ZmF_8gonAlKAGJ2DteI_mtDevObiFChGCcgej-LkdPs2NfbltLEn3KmB47o70mGBuSQ3WbY5xU9pE8liQ\" width=\"624\" height=\"107\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Through our exploratory study we unpacked how these Megatrends are shaping culture individually as well as generationally, nudging people to not just â€œreactâ€ to stressors but actively create a life free from them, in many cases triggering them to change, evolve in ways they had never done before, with plants, growing and gardening playing a key role across each of them.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin: 0pt -11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(231, 244, 238); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">OPENING THE CONSUMER WORLD</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin: 0pt -11pt 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(231, 244, 238); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Green-starved urban millennials who often feel an absence of nature, and start a journey of â€˜growing somethingâ€™ at home with a spot of green.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin: 0pt -11pt 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(231, 244, 238); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">They want to create bandwidth for their own needs, even if that means slowing down and being more selective of how they spend their time. They feel the need for a pause, plants offer that pause.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin: 0pt -11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(231, 244, 238); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In a world that they perceive to be increasingly relentless, unforgiving and destructive, they prioritise their wellbeing and act mindfully to ensure their personal growth.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin: 0pt -11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(231, 244, 238); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:571px;height:751px;\"><img alt=\"ugaoo_strat-consum\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/WUTVRe-d3IXRrhGgWNuVnE5Q2w8LqjvhBIQ8u-9q9jmyVcFIwySUtOksrjgBYpslLguGIyen63uj1d0oedddtre4EI2yb88snzi3ZXeyYVWIVwu2rXUko9w3rjp0Dh96C_JWbF6VOKvhymNfyRtdrNzjmBtKItMlBtRvLYYRvUz5pkThkdJp6ODFh3WyVA\" width=\"571\" height=\"751\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(15, 76, 54); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">THE NEED FOR A PAUSE</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">People are looking to create big and small, life-changing choices and habits to safeguard their personal time, state of mind and happiness over the normalised pressures &amp; pace of life that existed pre-pandemic.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">People today are not just looking to manage time, they are looking to pause. Plants are a Pause.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(15, 76, 54); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">THE SUSTAINABILITY STORY</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">People are learning and adopting more sustainable practices in their private lives. The bar is being pushed high by both consumers and influencers.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The perfect idea of sustainability is hard to attain but itâ€™s a journey to be made. People appreciate support in facilitating the mindset.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(15, 76, 54); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">THE POWER OF TRANSFORMATION AND GROWTH</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Plants change people. They mature and see the big picture in life. People grow with their plants. Our category is about personal growth and life-enhancement.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(15, 76, 54); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">EXPLORATION AND LEARNING</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The lockdown triggered personal reflection and self-exploration in Indians to pursue new interests, encouraging a DIY culture in our homes.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">â€œDoing things yourselfâ€ also became an in-road to sustainable practices</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(15, 76, 54); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">DECOR AND APPEARANCE</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Plants create â€˜energy spacesâ€™ rather than just decor spaces. They are objects of care, not just pretty objects.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">People are mindful of where they place their plants.</span></p><br><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:859px;height:320px;\"><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/hRhBE37TiQndNd4ZWVwpv93QwHnac3We3CikzrmL9mV1ru5T5j_h1-psPy0OwWH_MPyZQvSKaTqCWPJZO4RwntRPJw59O74QqJkSzjzvzzXn5CG72_MvPnuahNSt5XGLl3oFJZCUZ57DxkgemwLMCPSWBRoL5mqrqJ7y3MN1yRkZLxb8D2xbfIgGllusTw\" width=\"843.56045751634\" height=\"314.24836601307186\" style=\"margin-left:-5.542394642614538e-14px;margin-top:0px;\"></span><br><br></h2></span></blockquote></div><div class=\"photo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; width: 468.375px;\"></div></div></div></section></main></div>', 'about.png', 'BAYLEAF - About Us', '', '', 'Contact Us', 'banner.jpg', 'Feedbacks', '', '');

